headline: Is NextEra Energy Fairly Priced After Latest 5% Weekly Drop in 2025?
summary: If you are eyeing NextEra Energy’s stock right now, you are hardly alone. Investors everywhere are pondering whether this utility powerhouse deserves a place in their portfolios, especially after seeing the stock close recently at $72.09. With the shares fairly flat over the last month at 0.2% and year-to-date returns of just 0.7%, it is natural to wonder if there is value lurking beneath the surface or if the modest rebound is just a mirage.
